Where Your Family Comes Together


So much happens around your dining table from breakfast to homework, which is why our dining tables are designed for more than just eating. Our STORNÄS dining table, made of solid pine, can comfortably seat four and quickly be extended to entertain a party of six. Keep the conversations going with the INGATORP extendable table that can make space for more when needed. While our NORDEN gateleg table is perfect for two, lift both the drop-leaves to make space for a double-date. Most of our dining tables are resistant to sticky hands and the usual wear and tear.
